        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(local-container): clean stale docker claims on stop",
        "body": "## Summary\n- allow `crabbox stop --provider docker <lease-or-slug>` to clean a stale local-container claim when the backing container was removed outside Crabbox\n- keep normal resolve/status/run behavior strict when the container is missing, and preserve Docker context scoping for claim cleanup\n- add an optional build-tagged local-container Docker live smoke and document how to run it\n\n## Verification\n- `env -u CRABBOX_PROVIDER -u CRABBOX_CONFIG -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR_TOKEN -u CRABBOX_ADMIN_TOKEN go test ./internal/providers/localcontainer ./internal/cli`\n- `env -u CRABBOX_PROVIDER -u CRABBOX_CONFIG -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR_TOKEN -u CRABBOX_ADMIN_TOKEN go test ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `env -u CRABBOX_PROVIDER -u CRABBOX_CONFIG -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR_TOKEN -u CRABBOX_ADMIN_TOKEN go test -tags localcontainer ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `env -u CRABBOX_PROVIDER -u CRABBOX_CONFIG -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR_TOKEN -u CRABBOX_ADMIN_TOKEN .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n\n## Config and secrets\n- no new config keys or provider names\n- no secret handling changes\n- optional live smoke honors `CRABBOX_LOCAL_CONTAINER_E2E_IMAGE` for selecting a faster prebuilt test image\n\n## Screenshots\n- not applicable; CLI/provider behavior only\n",
